OL,3,CMet Office confirms Thursday is the
OL,4,Chottest start to May on record
OL,6,FThe UK has had its hottest ever start
OL,7,Fto May with temperatures soaring above
OL,8,F28 degrees Celsius at Kew Gardens in
OL,9,FLondon as, ITV News correspondent Ben
OL,10,FChapman reports.
OL,12,FThe UK has seen the warmest start to
OL,13,FMay on record as temperatures continue
OL,14,Fto soar, with firefighters battling
OL,15,Fwildfires and warnings over the
OL,16,Fdangers of open water swimming.
