OL,6,FFirefighters are battling a 2km
OL,7,Fmoorland blaze which broke out near
OL,8,FRipponden, West Yorkshire, on Thursday.
OL,10,FWest Yorkshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Fwas called at 12.15pm on Thursday to
OL,12,Freports of a fire off Oldham Road.
OL,14,FIt quickly spread in hot, dry weather
OL,15,Fand by mid-afternoon, 18 crews were at
OL,16,Fthe scene with support units from
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService.
