OL,6,F"We shouldn't be getting close to 30C
OL,7,Fhere in the UK on the first of May. We
OL,8,Fshouldn't be seeing our fourth
OL,9,Fconsecutive month of below average
OL,10,Frainfall. None of this should be
OL,11,Fhappening," she said.
OL,13,F"The fact is that, whilst adaptations
OL,14,Fcan be made to the way we live, a
OL,15,Frapidly changing climate is rapidly
OL,16,Fchanging the world as we know it.
