OL,6,F"The native wildlife and its habitat,
OL,7,Fthe way that we produce the resources
OL,8,Fthat we need, the way the travel, the
OL,9,Fway we care for the most vulnerable in
OL,10,Four society - even, gradually, the
OL,11,Fphysical size of the island that we
OL,12,Flive on as rising sea levels threaten
OL,13,Four shores.
OL,15,F"Yes, it is lovely to have warm, sunny
OL,16,Fdays. Of course it is. But not this
OL,17,Fwarm, not this often and not this
OL,18,Fearly. Globally, 2024 was the hottest
OL,19,Fyear on record. And that should be
OL,20,Fdeeply concerning for us all."
